<!doctype html>
<html lang="<%= lang %>">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>St. Matthew CCD &mdash; Faith Formation</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;0,700;1,400&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
</head>
<body>

<%- include('_topbar') %>

<main class="container py-4 app-shell mx-auto">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <div class="hero mb-4">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <span class="hero-eyebrow">School Year 2025–2026</span>
      <h1><%= t('app_title') %></h1>
      <p class="subtitle"><%= t('landing_focus_title') %> &mdash; <%= t('landing_focus_subtitle') %></p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Auth CTA -->
  <div class="page-card mb-4">
    <div class="card-body">
      <p class="mb-3" style="font-size:.92rem;color:var(--muted)"><%= t('secure_online') %></p>
      <% if (!user) { %>
        <p class="mb-3" style="font-size:.92rem;color:var(--muted)"><%= t('reg_requires_account') %></p>
      <% } %>
      <% if (user) { %>
        <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-2 align-items-center">
          <span class="badge badge-role badge-<%= user.role %>"><%= user.role %></span>
          <span style="font-size:.85rem;color:var(--muted)"><%= t('signed_in_as') %> <strong style="color:var(--ink-soft)"><%= user.email %></strong></span>
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/dashboard"><%= t('open_dashboard') %></a>
          <a class="btn btn-outline-success" href="/registration/new"><%= t('register_child') %></a>
          <a class="btn btn-outline-primary" href="/registration/adult"><%= t('register_adult') %></a>
          <a class="btn btn-outline-secondary" href="/logout"><%= t('logout') %></a>
        </div>
      <% } else { %>
        <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/signup"><%= t('create_account') %></a>
          <a class="btn btn-outline-primary" href="/login"><%= t('login') %></a>
        </div>
      <% } %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- About / Accordion -->
  <div class="page-card">
    <div class="card-header">
      <h2 class="h5">Faith Formation at St. Matthew Parish</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="card-body">
      <p style="font-size:.95rem">At St. Matthew Catholic Church, faith formation is more than a program&mdash;it is a journey of growing as disciples of Jesus Christ. Our parish seeks to help children, parents, and families deepen their relationship with Christ and live their Catholic faith in everyday life.</p>
      <p style="font-size:.95rem">Inspired by the vision of Family Faith Formation Catholic Ministries, St. Matthew Parish embraces a family-centered approach to faith formation, recognizing parents as the first and most important teachers of the faith.</p>

      <div class="accordion mt-3" id="faithFormationAccordion">
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <h2 class="accordion-header">
            <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseOne">
              A Family-Centered Vision
            </button>
          </h2>
          <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" data-bs-parent="#faithFormationAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              <p>Faith is best learned and lived within the family. Rather than seeing religious education as only a classroom experience for children, St. Matthew Parish supports families by providing:</p>
              <ul>
                <li>Formation opportunities for both parents and children</li>
                <li>Resources to help families practice and discuss their faith at home</li>
                <li>Parish gatherings that foster prayer, learning, and community</li>
              </ul>
              <p class="mb-0">This approach reflects the Church's teaching that the family is the <em>"domestic church,"</em> where the faith is first experienced and shared.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
          <h2 class="accordion-header">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTwo">
              Parish and Family Working Together
            </button>
          </h2>
          <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faithFormationAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              <p>Faith formation at St. Matthew Parish is a partnership between the parish community and the family. Families participate in:</p>
              <ul>
                <li>Periodic family catechesis gatherings</li>
                <li>Sacramental preparation programs</li>
                <li>Opportunities for prayer, fellowship, and service</li>
                <li>Faith-centered activities that strengthen family life and community bonds</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
          <h2 class="accordion-header">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree">
              Sacramental Preparation
            </button>
          </h2>
          <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faithFormationAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              <p>Preparation for the Sacraments&mdash;especially First Reconciliation, First Holy Communion, and Confirmation&mdash;is an important part of our faith formation process. Parents are actively involved through retreats, parish sessions, and home-based formation.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
          <h2 class="accordion-header">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseFour">
              Growing as Missionary Disciples
            </button>
          </h2>
          <div id="collapseFour" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faithFormationAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              <p>Through prayer, catechesis, community life, and service, we strive to help our parish community:</p>
              <ul>
                <li>Develop a personal relationship with Jesus Christ</li>
                <li>Grow in love for Sacred Scripture and the Sacraments</li>
                <li>Experience the support of the parish community</li>
                <li>Live the Gospel through service and witness</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p class="footer-note"><%= t('footer_note') %></p>
</main>

<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
